    "MissionGiver": "Ruto",
    "Title": "Ripe for the Taking",
    "Description": "Got some good news for you. As we speak, there\u2019s an automated facility that is churning out package after package of primo product that\u2019s pretty much ripe for the taking.\n\nAll you have to do is swoop down there, deal with a thug or two, grab whatever you can, and sell it for a huge profit. Shouldn\u2019t be a problem at all. And there are plenty of people around who would pay good creds to take product like that off your hands.\n\nSpeaking of credits, I\u2019m not gonna just give out the coordinates of this facility out of the kindness of my heart. I think it\u2019s only fair to ask a finder\u2019s fee for info this good.\n\nI wouldn\u2019t wait too long. Not sure how long the site will be left running.\n\n-Ruto",
